<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīmatribhuvanacakravartti śrīkulōttuṁggacōḍadēvara vijayarājyasaṁvatsaramulu 15 gu śrāhi śrīmanmahāmaṇḍalēśvara tribhuvanamallidēvacōḍamahārājulu śrīmanmahāmaṇḍalē śvara kulōttuṁggacōḍagoṁkkarājulunuṁ gammanāṁṭilōni koṭyadona tribhuvanamallaśrīkēśava dēvarakuṁ beddagaṁjāmu koṁḍoka gaṁjāmuṁ gaḍakuduru Uppa 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṟaṭla peralivāyuṁdoṟṟu gūravāḍa berasina yuppalamula Uppu yammina pahiṁḍivalana Āṣāḍa ba 13 guruvāramu modalugā māḍa reṁḍu vīsālu havibaliyarccanalakuṁ bātrapāguḍamulaku Ācaṁdrārkkatārakamugā niccitimi <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> madhvaṁśajaḥ paramahīpativaṁśajā vā pāpādapētamanasā bhuvi bhāvibhūpāḥ<supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yē pālayaṁtti mama
<lb n="3"/>dharmmamidaṁ samastaṁ tē<unclear>ṣā</unclear>mmayā viracitāṁjalirēṣa mūrdhni <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> svadattāṁ paradattāṁ vā yō harēti vasuṁddharā[ṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>*] ṣaṣṭhirvvaruṣasahasrāṇi viṣṭāyāṁ jāyatē krimi <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> bahubhirvvasudhā dattā bahubhiścānupālitā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yesya yesya tadā bhūmistasya tasya tadā phalaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">3</supplied> Akarasya karīkārō gōsahasravadhasmritaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> karapravrittivicchedō gōkōṭiphalamaśnute [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 4*]
</p>

